---
/* Section focused on clear, actionable support requests */
---

<section class="w-full py-32 px-6 md:px-12 bg-theme-base">
  <div class="max-w-6xl mx-auto">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-12 gap-16 items-start">
      
      {/* Left Column: Title & Intent */}
      <div class="lg:col-span-5">
        <span class="text-brand-gold font-sans text-xs uppercase tracking-[0.3em] mb-6 block font-semibold">
          What Support Makes Possible
        </span>
        <h2 class="font-serif text-4xl md:text-5xl text-theme mb-8 leading-tight">
          What We Are <br /> <span class="text-brand-gold italic">Asking For</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="p-6 bg-theme-surface border-l-2 border-brand-gold/50">
          <p class="font-sans text-theme-soft text-lg leading-relaxed italic">
            "This support would not be used for expansion, but for rebuilding a stable foundation."
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>

      {/* Right Column: Specific Needs */}
      <div class="lg:col-span-7 grid grid-cols-1 gap-6">
        
        {/* Need 1 */}
        <div class="p-8 border theme-card theme-card-hover rounded-lg group hover:border-brand-gold/30 transition-all duration-500">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
            <span class="font-serif text-3xl text-brand-gold/30 group-hover:text-brand-gold transition-colors italic">01</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-theme mb-3">Workshop Space</h3>
              <p class="font-sans text-theme-muted leading-relaxed">
                A small, dedicated environment to restart stable and professional production.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Need 2 */}
        <div class="p-8 border theme-card theme-card-hover rounded-lg group hover:border-brand-gold/30 transition-all duration-500">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
            <span class="font-serif text-3xl text-brand-gold/30 group-hover:text-brand-gold transition-colors italic">02</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-theme mb-3">Tools & Materials</h3>
              <p class="font-sans text-theme-muted leading-relaxed">
                The basic equipment and high-quality raw materials required for traditional Khatam craftsmanship.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

        {/* Need 3 */}
        <div class="p-8 border theme-card theme-card-hover rounded-lg group hover:border-brand-gold/30 transition-all duration-500">
          <div class="flex items-start gap-6">
            <span class="font-serif text-3xl text-brand-gold/30 group-hover:text-brand-gold transition-colors italic">03</span>
            <div>
              <h3 class="font-serif text-2xl text-theme mb-3">Foundational Support</h3>
              <p class="font-sans text-theme-muted leading-relaxed">
                Support, grant, or sponsorship to cover initial setup costs and ensure continuity during the transition.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>

      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>